OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSchool summer holidays     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcould be cut by one week   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, School summer holidays in Wales will be
OL,6, cut by a week with the possibility of  
OL,7, moving to a four-week break in future  
OL,8, under new Welsh government plans.      
OL,10,FThe changes would see the week-long    
OL,11,FOctober half term break extended to a  
OL,12,Ffortnight.                             
OL,14,FIt is claimed the change would benefit 
OL,15,Fdisadvantaged pupils and boost the     
OL,16,Fwellbeing of students and staff.       
OL,18,FBut a union said there was no evidence 
OL,19,Fthe changes would help children's      
OL,20,Feducation.                             
